data.description: Drastically reduced price!, priced to sale!, seller motivated!, buy with no money down!!!  Property appraises for more, you can add 6% seller concessions to a FHA loan or 3% with a Conventional Fanniemae Loan, also, lender could help with a county down payment assistant program from $8k to $28K depending on buyer's qualifications.  Beautiful 5/2 1/2,, 2 story home at BAYWINDS OF FLORES, Homestead FL, Resort like club house, large gym, gated community, brand new accordion shutters, brand new A/C unit, in & out, new stainless-steel appliances, remodeled, a must see!, etc.
